short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple to use GUI interface that provides an easier way to make Chrome DevTools Extensions

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple to use GUI interface that provides an easier way to make Chrome DevTools Extensions. If you are a developer trying to create your own Chrome DevTools Extensions, or you want to just make a little one to help out in testing your own web application, you should use epack.
